一年<br />\n3.商場成日都有場攞黎賣-貨<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係積左d舊貨賣唔出想清，真係唔會入場賣"},{"pid":"ea6e449f7ca8084c355ff4a0aefb0c179f2bc037","tid":57222,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"盡量守返規矩"},{"pid":"c04e47689786a932366e9abc1273159386abddb4","tid":57222,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"美食展在工展會後唔夠一個月<br />\n美食展有既野，大部分在工展會都有<br />\n所以好多人去完工展會就唔會再去美食展，就算去都唔會點買野"},{"pid":"30f030d93dea141702f37239fecf311ae152f472","tid":57222,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個夾壞左呀</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/10-28-2015/Fy4d4J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F10-28-2015%2FFy4d4J.gif&h=318a2ec0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d1efa30d0e9eea2a78deafc25776435cac5fca","tid":57222,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"你個野壞左丫～"},{"pid":"1bbbfed62842f43b8ff9f9d5d4e638f32a05872d","tid":57222,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個夾壞左呀</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/10-28-2015/Fy4d4J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F10-28-2015%2FFy4d4J.gif&h=318a2ec0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa